lenders.occupational_info:
Running a little short and need quick cash? It happens with everyone and the payday loan program at Blue Copper Capital is here for you. Get up to $1500 in quick cash with out a credit check. It doesn’t matter if a short term loan is needed to pay bills, repair your car, pay for an unplanned expense or just some money to make things a bit easier; Blue Copper Capital certainly can help.

The pay day loan is a short term loan which is paid back on your next pay day. With no credit check they only qualifications are to be 18 or over, employed gainfully as well as having an active bank account. You are eligible for 30%-50% of your net pay and get the cash right away.

You can meet us at one of our locations or better yet, we’ll come to you! Blue Copper Capital offers a quick and headache free experience. We will do the loan on your schedule. Simply no need to stand in line and take up time out of your day. We make it simple for you to choose Blue Copper Capital for your borrowing needs.
